headline: Tetra Tech Wins $416M Civil Engineering Contracts From USACE
summary: TTEK clinches three $416 million multiple-award deals from the USACE to provide technical services for facilities and sites across the Indo-Pacific region.

headline: Allegion Named 2025 Gallup Exceptional Workplace Award Winner
summary: DUBLIN, March 19, 2025--Allegion plc (NYSE: ALLE), a leading global security products and solutions provider, has received the 2025 Gallup Exceptional Workplace Award (GEWA) for the second consecutive year. This award recognizes the most engaged workplace cultures in the world — organizations that achieve more by helping their employees focus on what they do best.
